text:
="preserve">Freddie James Prinze (born Frederick Karl Pruetzel; June 22-1954 - January 29, 1977) is an American stand-up comedian and actor.
Early life.
Prinze was born in New York City to Edward Karl Pruetzel and Aurea Elana Ruiz. His father is German and His mother is Puerto Rican.
Personal life.
Prinze married Kathy Barber and had a son Freddie Prinze, Jr. in 1976.
